.TH "TODOPRO FOCUS" "1" "2026-02-27" "1.0.0" "todopro focus Manual"
.SH NAME
todopro\-focus \- Focus mode — Pomodoro timer
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B todopro focus
[OPTIONS] COMMAND [ARGS]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
Focus mode — Pomodoro timer
.SH COMMANDS
.PP
\fBstart\fP
  Start a focus session on a task.
  See \fBtodopro focus-start(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBstart\fP command.
.PP
\fBresume\fP
  Resume a paused or interrupted focus session.
  See \fBtodopro focus-resume(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBresume\fP command.
.PP
\fBstop\fP
  Stop the current focus session.
  See \fBtodopro focus-stop(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBstop\fP command.
.PP
\fBstatus\fP
  Show current focus session status.
  See \fBtodopro focus-status(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBstatus\fP command.
.PP
\fBcycle\fP
  Start an automatic Pomodoro cycle with...
  See \fBtodopro focus-cycle(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBcycle\fP command.
.PP
\fBtemplates\fP
  List available focus session templates.
  See \fBtodopro focus-templates(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBtemplates\fP command.
.PP
\fBtemplate\fP
  Create or delete a custom focus template.
  See \fBtodopro focus-template(1)\fP for full documentation on the \fBtemplate\fP command.
